Somali: Korka mid kamida waqooyiga buuraha Makka, waxaa aduunka intiisa kale ka xadidan godka. 
English: A car bomb killed a Saudi Arabian pilgrim in Mecca, the holy city of Islam.
clean_output: A car bomb killed a Saudi Arabian pilgrim in Mecca, the holy city of Islam.
